title: Let's Watch TV: Keep Sweet, Pray and Obey
description:
This week, Joe and Fran get uninvited from their next family reunion for breaking HIPPA laws before they get into one of the craziest (and worst) series they've watched yet! Keep Sweet, Pray and Obey is a Netflix series exploring the polygamous Fundamentalist Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints and its almost too much for even Joe to handle.
